http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: Welcome to Delaware's Statewide Recommended Curriculum in Physical Education. This document represents years of dedicated contribution from classroom teachers, curriculum specialists, academicians, higher education staff and Delaware Department of Education specialists and associates. The standards as they appear in this document were reviewed and clarified to reflect the needs as established in Delaware. The  recommendations called for the standards to be clear, well defined, and user friendly.
